verses.text: We give thanks unto thee, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God; We give thanks, for thy name is near: Men tell \w of|strong="H4210"\w* thy wondrous works.
When \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w shall|strong="H8034"\w* find \w the|strong="H3034"\w* set time, \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w will|strong="H8034"\w* judge uprightly.

\w The|strong="H3588"\w* earth \w and|strong="H3947"\w* \w all|strong="H3947"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* inhabitants thereof \w are|strong="H8199"\w* dissolved: \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3588"\w* \w set|strong="H4150"\w* \w up|strong="H3947"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* pillars \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w it|strong="H3588"\w*. \qs [Selah\qs*

\w I|strong="H3605"\w* said unto \w the|strong="H3605"\w* arrogant, Deal not arrogantly; \w And|strong="H3427"\w* \w to|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wicked, Lift not \w up|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* horn:

\w Lift|strong="H7311"\w* not \w up|strong="H7311"\w* \w your|strong="H7311"\w* \w horn|strong="H7161"\w* \w on|strong="H7161"\w* \w high|strong="H7311"\w*; Speak not \w with|strong="H7161"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* stiff neck.

\w For|strong="H7311"\w* neither from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* east, nor from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* west, Nor \w yet|strong="H1696"\w* from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* south, \add cometh\add* \w lifting|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w*.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w is|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* judge: \w He|strong="H3588"\w* putteth \w down|strong="H3588"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w*, \w and|strong="H4057"\w* \w lifteth|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w* \w another|strong="H3808"\w*.

\w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w in|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* hand \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w Jehovah|strong="H3068"\w* \w there|strong="H2088"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cup, \w and|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* wine foameth; \w It|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* full \w of|strong="H8199"\w* mixture, \w and|strong="H2088"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* poureth out \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w same|strong="H2088"\w*: \w Surely|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* dregs thereof, all \w the|strong="H3588"\w* wicked \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* earth \w shall|strong="H2088"\w* drain \w them|strong="H3588"\w*, \w and|strong="H2088"\w* drink \w them|strong="H3588"\w*.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* declare \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w ever|strong="H2088"\w*, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* sing \w praises|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Jacob.

\w All|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* wicked also \w will|strong="H3290"\w* \w I|strong="H5046"\w* cut off; \w But|strong="H3290"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* horns \w of|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* righteous \w shall|strong="H3290"\w* \w be|strong="H5769"\w* \w lifted|strong="H3290"\w* up.
